data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS! Welcome to your home in the country. Walk into a large open entry facing a formal dining or living area with a 2 sided fireplace to the large casual living area. You will immediately notice the large windows in both living areas that add great natural sunlight to the house and give you a beautiful view of the 1 acre lot. The kitchen is open to the casual dining and large living area. Walk-in laundry room with a sink and shelving. The master bedroom and bathroom are huge with a jetted tub, 2 sinks, walk-in shower and walk-in closet. The study across from the master has great character with wainscoting, wood look tile floor and built in desk. Oversized 2 car garage, plenty of room for 2 large vehicles and yard equipment. In-ground sprinkler system. Half wrap-around porch in the backyard with a beautifully built shaded area. Perfect for entertaining. Storm shelter in backyard 6-8ppl. Brand new roof and guttering September 2023 (currently being installed).
